

# type(scope): summary   e.g. fix(audio): stop crackling
#
# types:  add, fix, update, remove, refactor
# scope:  the module/dir touched, e.g. hyprland, steam, firefox, audio, network
#
# Keep the summary short and in imperative mood ("add", not "added").
# One change per commit where practical - split unrelated changes into
# separate commits instead of joining them with commas.
#
# Optional: add a blank line below, then a sentence or two on *why*
# if it's not obvious from the change itself.
